text: Ovidiu Buidoso (born 13 July 1987) is a Romanian gymnast. He competed in five events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dubăsari District, Transnistria
